# Artifact Virtual Dashboard Implementation Plan

## Project Overview
Create a comprehensive, production-grade dashboard for Artifact Virtual that covers all aspects of the platform including AI ecosystems, blockchain development, knowledge foundations, quantum computing, and research tools.

## Implementation Checklist

### Phase 1: Core Architecture and Navigation
- [x] Create project structure
- [x] Set up routing and navigation
- [ ] Fix dead-end pages (Projects, Settings)
- [ ] Implement advanced responsive layout
- [x] Create theme provider with dark/light mode
- [ ] Redesign color scheme (avoid blue, standardize colors)
- [ ] Implement AVA assistant floating chat bubble
- [ ] Create comprehensive settings page

### Phase 2: AI Ecosystems Enhancement
- [ ] Create AI playground with langchain and langgraph integration
- [ ] Implement workspace for chat components with add/remove functionality
- [ ] Add model selection dropdown for each component
- [ ] Expand provider list with installation CLI
- [ ] Rename "AutoRound" to "Model Quantization"
- [ ] Add support for additional quantization techniques
- [ ] Rename "MCP" to "Communication Protocols"
- [ ] Create detailed protocol configuration page
- [ ] Add server types for web2/web3 connections

### Phase 3: System Management
- [ ] Create comprehensive system metrics dashboard
- [ ] Implement hardware monitoring (RAM, GPU, cooling)
- [ ] Add file management system (upload, view, delete)
- [ ] Create dedicated storage management interface
- [ ] Implement performance analytics
- [ ] Add system health monitoring
- [ ] Create backup and restore functionality

### Phase 4: Knowledge Foundations Enhancement
- [ ] Improve dataset management with multi-format support
- [ ] Add compilation tools for creating trainable datasets
- [ ] Enhance library integration with uploaded documents
- [ ] Implement advanced search capabilities
- [ ] Create visualization tools for knowledge relationships
- [ ] Add version control for knowledge assets

### Phase 5: Blockchain Development Enhancement
- [ ] Create multi-wallet configuration across chains
- [ ] Add support for all major blockchain networks
- [ ] Implement NFT minting and management
- [ ] Create web3 wallet provider integration
- [ ] Enhance network configuration with add/remove functionality
- [ ] Implement comprehensive blockchain explorer
- [ ] Add transaction monitoring and management

### Phase 6: IDE Integration
- [ ] Create lightweight IDE with Hardhat and Rust support
- [ ] Implement file manager with sliding panes
- [ ] Add code preview functionality
- [ ] Create template library for smart contracts
- [ ] Implement syntax highlighting and code completion
- [ ] Add testing and debugging tools
- [ ] Create deployment pipeline integration

### Phase 7: Applications Restructuring
- [ ] Split into Projects, Applications, and Research sections
- [ ] Create detailed project pages with contribution info
- [ ] Implement application shortcuts and management
- [ ] Create research section with drafting and notes
- [ ] Add publication library
- [ ] Implement project tracking and management
- [ ] Create collaboration tools

### Phase 8: Quantum Computing Integration
- [ ] Create quantum computing dashboard
- [ ] Implement algorithm management
- [ ] Add simulation tools
- [ ] Create results visualization
- [ ] Implement export and comparison functionality
- [ ] Add quantum resource estimation
- [ ] Create quantum circuit designer

### Phase 9: Advanced Features
- [ ] Implement AVA virtual assistant integration
- [ ] Create advanced analytics dashboard
- [ ] Add workflow automation tools
- [ ] Implement CI/CD pipeline integration
- [ ] Create collaborative editing features
- [ ] Add advanced security controls
- [ ] Implement audit logging

### Phase 10: Testing and Optimization
- [ ] Perform comprehensive testing across all modules
- [ ] Optimize performance for large datasets
- [ ] Implement error handling and recovery
- [ ] Create fallback mechanisms
- [ ] Perform security audit
- [ ] Optimize for various devices and screen sizes
- [ ] Implement accessibility features

### Phase 11: Documentation and Deployment
- [ ] Create comprehensive user documentation
- [ ] Add inline help and tooltips
- [ ] Create video tutorials
- [ ] Prepare deployment package
- [ ] Set up CI/CD pipeline
- [ ] Deploy to production environment
- [ ] Implement monitoring and alerting
